#: .\pages\templates\pages\home.html:163
msgid ""
"A simple, defined path so you always know what happens next — before you "
"visit, during your appointment, and when you leave with your documents."
msgstr ""
"Hannaan fudud oo qeexan si aad mar walba u ogaato waxa xiga — ka hor "
"booqashada, inta ballankaagu socdo, iyo marka aad dukumeentiyadaada la baxdo."

