#: .\pages\templates\pages\home.html:193
msgid ""
"Whether you need a single affidavit or a stack of business papers, Himilo "
"Notary brings the same attention to detail — explaining requirements in "
"plain language and making your visit efficient."
msgstr ""
"Haddii aad u baahan tahay hal dhaar-caddeyn ama xirmo waraaqo ganacsi ah, "
"Himilo Nootaayo waxay keentaa taxaddar isku mid ah — iyadoo shuruudaha ku "
"sharxaysa luqad cad, booqashadaadana ka dhigaysa mid hufan."

